  "texts": [
    "In this section we present the guidelines provided to human annotators, as explicated in Figure 7.",
    "Annotators were instructed to assign labels of 0 or 1 according to the presence of specific characteristics within the text.",
    "To mitigate the potential ambiguity inherent in the subjective nature of these characteristics, additional clarifications were included.",
    "Furthermore, we integrated \"Gender bias\" and \"Social bias\" into a single \"Toxicity\" metric because of significant correlation between these variables.",
    "Table 2 presents the correlation between human assessments and GPT-4 evaluations, featuring the average F1 scores of GPT-4 alongside those of three independent annotators."
